- 'Explorers' refers to users who accessed the sizing charts; 
- 'Treasure maps' are metaphorical representations of sizing charts in the clothing database; 
- 'Navigated regions' refers to the regions associated with the sizing charts; 
- 'Last uncovered the treasures' means the most recent access dates for each chart.

